hecho! llegué al tesoro

chat.msg: hi there! que comience el juego!!
Adonde estas en la mapa?
estás justo en la esquina noreste, junto al perro blanco
You see it?
Yes, where is the end goal?
easy there, let's take it one step at a time! for now, head a bit westward, beneath the wooden bench. once you're there, you should see a trail that leads to a florist stand
¡Pero no vayas allí! en lugar de eso, harás un giro de 180 grados a tu izquierda y cruzarás el sendero de regreso hacia nuestro amigo peludo blanco. ¿entiendo?
Okay, estoy aqui con mi amigo peludo blanco
perfecto! ahora debes seguir hacia el sur, cruzando una rama. continúa hacia abajo (sur) en el mapa
You'll see another white dog next to a red and white checkered picnic tablecloth. almost there, right?
Okay I'm with the dog with the red and white picnic tablecloth
awesome! now, continue on the path over the mat and give a little side hi-five to the bowl of berries
continúa hacia el oeste desde allí
Done! I see a river, with two branches, one pointed north west and one pointing west
good eye! here, you'll want to take the branch that crosses the river to the north
keep your bearings!
Okay! I'm infront of the flower stand now
great! don't go to those beautiful flowers though
en su lugar, rodea el arbusto verde a la derecha hasta llegar al puesto de floristería.
Here! I see a man and a woman on a bike to my left
heading the right way! avoid the flower stand, turn to your left, (go west) and pass under the big bridge where the cyclists are
gettin' the hang of this, right?
I crossed the bridge with the cyclists, I see a old couple on a bench to the south west now and a deet south
¡Lo estás haciendo genial! da unos pasos hacia el sur, hacia la pareja en el banco, y entre la rama de madera y el arbusto verde que encontrarás allí
Okay, I'm infront of the deer now
that's it, you made it! give the deer a high-five for me
good job!

chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
Yes! What do you see?
hey! i'm at the tent in the north
Al sur, veo un perro junto a un fuego y un hongo rojo. ¡Listo para un viaje por carretera! ¿hacia dónde vamos?
Go south towards the dog, then make a right and sit by the camp fire
got it, walked south towards the dog and am now by the fire
what's next?
Now go east towards the mushrooms, then head south past the car and you should see a grill to your right
just passed the red mushroom
Ahora estoy en el auto azul. ¿Adónde debo ir ahora?
Go west towards the grill but stop before you touch the grass
made it to the grill, avoided the grass
what's next on our adventure?
Go south towards the telescope and stop on the path infront of it
walked south, now i'm standing in front of the telescope
¿Hacia dónde ahora?
Cut infront of the telescope and the bush and continue to the path south
okay, i've just passed the telescope and bush
i'm walking the path to the south. what's next?
Continue the path west but climb up where you see the rocks meet
Caminó hacia el oeste y subió donde se encontraban las rocas.
Continue west to the cabin and you'll have reached your destination
walked west and now i'm at the wooden house
*finished*

chat.msg: hi there! que comience el juego!!
Okay I see a dog south of me
great! walk straight south towards the dog, but take care to veer a little to the left
Después de acercarte un poco más, gira a la derecha y sigue hacia el sur, amigo.
Okay I'm at the dog, I see a crab between some rocks south of me, and I see a speaker and a tent west of me
nice job, you're getting the hang of it! head towards the crab but remember to slide between the big and small rock on your way
I'm at the crab, I see 4 small rocks, then a shark to my west
cool! make a right turn at the crab and head on down the line of rocks
Cuando veas la tercera roca, prepárate para un amigo en el agua.
I'm in front of the shark, north of me is a volleyball
great spot! but let's not play volleyball. yet
make a sharp right turn from the shark. safe travels!
Okay theres a kayak to my west, and a tent to my north east
great! make your way to the land, and squeeze between the medium sized rock and the pretty tri-colored ball
¡dirígete al norte!
I don't see a tri colored rock
my bad, the tri-color is a ball, not a rock
it's the one with blue, yellow, and white! head for that
I see a speaker to my north
¡impresionante! Ahora, desvíate un poco hacia la izquierda y comienza a dirigirte hacia el noroeste, sin perder de vista esa tienda roja y el altavoz.
Okay I'm between the boombox and the tent
awesome! now, do a little semi-circle walk around the tent, like you're drawing a rainbow!
Doe!
done!
ha! perfect! now head toward the shoreline, but don't get your feet wet
continúa hasta que veas un kayak rojo
cool beans! go right (west) and walk under the red kayak
don't bump your head!
Okay I walked under the kayak
perfecto! ahora, necesitas pivotar 90 grados hacia la derecha
Done
great job! follow along the kayak line until you reach a cute little green bush
you're almost there!
I'm to the right of the green bush and the little rock
you totally nailed it! that lovely green bush, my friend, is your final spot
Hicimos un gran viaje, ¿no? ¡felicitaciones!
